description: A busy day at the office. I interviewed 14 people today, it was terrible. On the other hand, I had more opportunities to check-out some nice boys. They mostly did not appreciate my special interest in them, only one was willing to go the extra mile to get the job.  He was a high school drop-out, in the Czech Republic that means you´re pretty much screwed. He tried to make a career as a bartender and a waiter but he quit because of low salary. He looked very optimistic and ambitious, maybe too much. The registration threw him off balance for a minute. I tried to play my usual role of an emphatic friend who wants to help. He resisted, but eventually he agreed to take off his T-shirt. I love when boys take care of their body, it was such a nice view...
title: Dirty Scout 36
